Dactyloscopy is an exact science, without the possibility of error, which can play a key role in deciding crimes.
In addition to identifying the corpses, these people help in the investigation of crimes such as theft or murder and confirm the identity of the captured persons.
When caught, a lot of delinquents present false papers or have no papers at all.
We'll take their fingerprints and search the database.
